      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，ELB作为统一网关。那订单服务和支付服务之间的数据存储怎么安排？我看到有Redis和数据库的需求，是不是要单独抽一个存储层？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "order_service",
        "payment_service",
        "redis",
        "db",
        "storage"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，存储层要独立出来。订单服务用Redis做缓存，同时连学生数据库；支付服务直接对接存储层。另外成绩同步服务也要纳入，它跟支付服务有交互。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "order_service",
        "redis",
        "db",
        "Education_StudentDB",
        "payment_service",
        "Education_GradeSync",
        "storage"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我把存储层做成子图，里面放Redis和DB，方向设为TB。网关、API服务、存储三类节点用不同颜色区分：网关用浅红色，API服务用橙色，存储用绿色，这样层级清晰。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "storage",
        "redis",
        "db",
        "gateway",
        "api",
        "storage"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "颜色方案可以。不过确认一下流向：用户调用ELB后，ELB应该能路由到订单服务和支付服务两个分支，对吧？还有内容CDN是独立节点，从ELB直接连过去。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "user",
        "ELB",
        "order_service",
        "payment_service",
        "Education_ContentCDN"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认，ELB到order_service、payment_service、ContentCDN都有连线。那学生数据库和课堂服务的归属呢？我看代码里标注有些混乱，需要统一。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ELB",
        "order_service",
        "payment_service",
        "Education_ContentCDN",
        "Education_StudentDB",
        "Education_ClassroomService"
      ],
